<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Congratulations My Love ❤️</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 400px;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #ff4b5c;
    }

    .heart {
      font-size: 40px;
      animation: heartbeat 1s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes heartbeat {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .btn {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: none;
      background: #ff4b5c;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 25px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #e8434f;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="heart">❤️</div>
    <h1>Congratulations My Love!</h1>
    <p>
      I am so proud of you for your new job! 🎉<br><br>
      Your hard work, dedication, and passion have paid off.
      This is just the beginning of amazing things ahead.
    </p>
    <p>
      Keep shining and chasing your dreams ✨<br>
      I will always be your biggest supporter ❤️
    </p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="showMessage()">Click for a Surprise</button>
  </div>

  <script>
    function showMessage() {
      alert("I love you so much ❤️ I'm incredibly proud of you!");
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
